reviewText: I love this show!! I wish they still made travel shows like this. I watch it over and over.

This dvd has a very clear picture, shows all the highlights of Bellagio, from the entrance to rooms and shops, also includes views of other landmarks on Las Vegas strip, but without mayor details, there's a lady narrating the visit and short interaction with hotel personnel, I wish there were many more episodes on Vegas hotels in this series.
I love these great hotel dvd's, especially the one's featuring Las Vegas, reminds me of the sights I saw when I was there last year, beautiful.
This dvd was definitely not quality.  I think it was an amateur recording.  Very disppointing.  We order a set of three and it was a complete waste of money.
